entries.journal_entry_description: Another of the stolen Gungan artifacts is in the possession of the Muskeg.
entries.journal_entry_title: Recover the Gungan Artifact Stolen by the Muskeg
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Fight Muskeg Anarchists and see if they have the artifact.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: None of da Muskeg Anarchists had da artifact. Try da Muskeg Extremists next.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Attack Muskeg extremists and find out if they have the artifact.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Da Muskeg extremists didn't have da artifact eider. Maybe da Muskeg reactionariin' have it.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Assault Muskeg reactionaries and determine if they have the artifact.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Hmm. None of da henchmen had da artifact. Maybe 'tis actually wid da leader dissen time.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Maybe their leader has the artifact. It could happen.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Defeat Flossin Noz, a Muskeg Zealot Chief
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Return to Boss Nass with the artifact.
